   LES CONTEMPLATIONS (LIVRES I A IV) - VICTOR HUGO - &lt;p
   style=&quot;margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm;
   text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span
   style=&quot;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span
